body:
### Welcome!
My name is Nathan Dalal, a current senior at the Harker School.

I am an aspiring computer programmer and I am very new to website development.
I have prior experience in Java, C, FORTRAN, and R, and am looking to become proficient in HTML5, CSS, and JavaScript.
That's why I made this website!

```
while (nathan.moreToLearn())
   nathan.explore();
```

See you soon!
